sources.title: SunsetCarsonRidesAgain
sources.description: Sunset Carson is trying to raise money for a new school and his partner Sam Webster (John L. Cason) is out to stop him. When Carson plans a benefit prize-fight, Webster plans to make off with the proceeds.
